IDD M&A TRANSACTIONS contains information on publicly announced
transactions involving a merger, acquisition, leveraged buy-out,
divestiture, stock purchase, tender offer, self tender, share
repurchase, or other major transaction.  All transactions of $1
million or more, transactions that involve the acquisition of at
least 5% of a company, and transactions with an undisclosed dollar
amount are included.  The primary focus is on U.S. companies, but
transactions involving non-U.S. companies are covered if the
transactions are reported in the U.S. press.  IDD M&A TRANSACTIONS
is updated monthly and contains the complete file, covering 1984
to the present, on a single disc.  An annual subscription is
$14,595.
 
For further information contact: Marketing Department, Dialog
Information Services, Inc., 3460 Hillview Avenue, Palo Alto, CA
94304 (800) 334-2564.
 
 
